{"tid":33544,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"請教日本樓市爆破的原因","createTime":"2016-12-11T00:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T08:35:06.000Z","uid":39195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1403ec7f60e60974fdbc936d01f9f1278d565a","tid":33544,"uid":39195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T00:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/082135_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F082135_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f8461e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5544425ec93deba93a3ebd5f795b33df1edf163","tid":33544,"uid":27166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:06:31.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"912d2f0b977b7366124e5ac2ae4ae450601256ff","tid":33544,"uid":42387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T01:09:28.000Z","msg":"留名學野😆😆😆"},{"pid":"ea7052543d88106ec14d1d31b2fc708cb0051b60","tid":33544,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:01:39.000Z","msg":"推pish"},{"pid":"55c4c6fdd486341e564de722a7bf3dee9aa719a0","tid":33544,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"求詳細解釋"},{"pid":"46cdd38206890aa7e2fa1c26ba7e26495296f991","tid":33544,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"要由廣場協議開始講起"},{"pid":"047d43f7e957c35ee800492c5a15f78d17bd712a","tid":33544,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要由廣場協議開始講起</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea06411f04c4eeb16f8ce2b8cf732d719bf4b79","tid":33544,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:35:14.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3cde68f81dee9e87f329872290ff7ea40d62c4c3","tid":33544,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:44:29.000Z","msg":"多撚謝香港人"},{"pid":"aac0ec715666c93ff3f06e87cf77eecc36c3b0cd","tid":33544,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多撚謝香港人</blockquote><br />\n願聞其詳"},{"pid":"7c6370c575a187142f9b8d6c45cfbb5f77cdcd28","tid":33544,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T06:28:50.000Z","msg":"Wiki 咪有囉 （日版）"},{"pid":"1e2fe4f8cf6bdd2dd3ae848fa57214c46b668151","tid":33544,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Wiki 咪有囉 （日版）</blockquote><br />\n有冇link?"},{"pid":"1730628b0f19d1d478dba15c80b0a90acd15fca3","tid":33544,"uid":25787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Wiki 咪有囉 （日版）</blockquote><br />\n有冇link?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你WIKI &quot;廣場協議&quot;就有相關既LINK。<br />\n<br />\n講晒成件事夠寫幾千字既論文，但基本上，個開始係由1985年9月簽廣場協議開始。<br />\n<br />\n之後美元：日元匯率由1:240 去到 1: 120左右<br />\n<br />\n由於貨幣升值，大量資金湧入，日本既出口受大打擊，同時推高日本資產價格。（樓市，地價高升，同早幾年既支那有啲似）<br />\n<br />\n出口受打擊，但資產價格上升，好容易就會出現一個現象：不務正業<br />\n<br />\n企業家唔去做實業改為走去炒賣土地，房屋（淨係東京一地既價值夠買起成個美國既企業等等）<br />\n<br />\n越來越多人不務正業，借錢都去買樓／土地搏升值（係咪好熟口面呢？）<br />\n<br />\n當樓價同土地價格去到一個無法支持既位，就會好似鬱金香狂熱咁個個都沽而唔買。沽唔到貨既，好多都係借按揭去買天價樓（係咪又係好熟口面呢？）就要供3代。<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講個故事就係咁上下，DETAIL要睇好多文先可以詳細了解時序。"},{"pid":"d0db324beeff18e7949fb47dfc7f6daf50fba1a9","tid":33544,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Wiki 咪有囉 （日版）</blockquote><br />\n有冇link?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你WIKI &quot;廣場協議&quot;就有相關既LINK。<br />\n<br />\n講晒成件事夠寫幾千字既論文，但基本上，個開始係由1985年9月簽廣場協議開始。<br />\n<br />\n之後美元：日元匯率由1:240 去到 1: 120左右<br />\n<br />\n由於貨幣升值，大量資金湧入，日本既出口受大打擊，同時推高日本資產價格。（樓市，地價高升，同早幾年既支那有啲似）<br />\n<br />\n出口受打擊，但資產價格上升，好容易就會出現一個現象：不務正業<br />\n<br />\n企業家唔去做實業改為走去炒賣土地，房屋（淨係東京一地既價值夠買起成個美國既企業等等）<br />\n<br />\n越來越多人不務正業，借錢都去買樓／土地搏升值（係咪好熟口面呢？）<br />\n<br />\n當樓價同土地價格去到一個無法支持既位，就會好似鬱金香狂熱咁個個都沽而唔買。沽唔到貨既，好多都係借按揭去買天價樓（係咪又係好熟口面呢？）就要供3代。<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講個故事就係咁上下，DETAIL要睇好多文先可以詳細了解時序。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港97時咪試過，所以依家銀行按揭無以前咁鬆"},{"pid":"af8e1f961add82152a3bbca60396542ba36e31b9","tid":33544,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:35:06.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}